        <ArticleTitle>cAMP-dependent protein kinase A and the dynamics of epithelial cell surface domains: moving membranes to keep in shape.</ArticleTitle>
        <Pagination>
          <StartPage>146</StartPage>
          <EndPage>155</EndPage>
